### Test Production API (Vercel)

### Check production server status
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/

### Register a new user (Production)
POST https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "produser",
  "email": "prod@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "fullName": "Production User"
}

### Login (Production)
POST https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "prod@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Get all users (Production)
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/auth/users

### Get current user (Production - need token)
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ========== PRODUCTS ==========

### Get all products
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/products

### Get products with pagination
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/products?page=1&limit=10

### Get products by category
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/products?category=Electronics

### Search products
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/products?search=laptop

### Get single product
GET https://backend-node-lilac-seven.vercel.app/api/products/1

